.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Updates the specified boot volume’s display name, defined tags, and free\-form tags.
.SH USAGE
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
oci bv boot\-volume update [OPTIONS]
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
